// Each task i has processing time t[i] and deadline d[i].
// All tasks must be done. Lateness of task i = max(0, finish_time - d[i]).
// Minimize the MAXIMUM lateness across all tasks.
// Input: n, then n pairs (t[i], d[i])
// Example: n=3, tasks={(3,6),(2,8),(1,9)}  => output: 0
// Example: n=3, tasks={(3,4),(2,2),(1,6)}  => output: 1

